    for food_name, serving_size, calories, carbs, protein, fat, vit_c, image_url in food_data:

        # Add nutrient associations
        food_nutrients = [
            FoodNutrient(food_id=food.id, nutrient_id=get_nutrient_id('Calories'), amount=calories),
            FoodNutrient(food_id=food.id, nutrient_id=get_nutrient_id('Carbohydrates'), amount=carbs),
